Package: Kifidi
Type: Package
Title: Summary Table and Means Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Oswald",
                  family = "Omuron",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "oswaldomuron@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Oswald Omuron <oswaldomuron@gmail.com>
Description: 
    Provides two key functions to work with environmental and ecological data:
    - 'summarize_data()' allows users to summarize datasets based on selected grouping variables, returning a summary object.
    - 'plot_means()' creates bar plots with optional error bars from the summarized data.
